## Limitations

The findings presented in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of media influence. The complexity of media effects, influenced by numerous intervening variables, makes it challenging to isolate specific impacts. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of media technologies means that ongoing research is necessary to fully understand their effects on individuals and society.

